Hrmbl. Tags are getting eaten by the blog app. Correction: To do this, append this to your pom.xml:

	&lt;repositories&gt;
		&lt;repository&gt;
			&lt;id&gt;maven2-repository.dev.java.net&lt;/id&gt;
			&lt;name&gt;Java.net Repository for Maven&lt;/name&gt;
			&lt;url&gt;http://download.java.net/maven/2/&lt;/url&gt;
		&lt;/repository&gt;
	&lt;/repositories&gt;
